RM / SIGINT (operator-driven)\n- All providers durably out (per ddx-aede917d quota pause/resume — workers pause+probe, not exit)\n- No providers configured at all (fatal config error)\n- --once explicitly requested\n- --poll-interval=0 explicitly requested",
